  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n\r\n## Problem \r\nWhen `Appearance` on status app is set to `System` (it is default) if light mode changed to dark (automatically, i.e. from device settings or manually) app needs to relaunch to apply mode.\r\nCan affect a lot of users, as by default devices are changing mode automatically (day -> night).\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nI can see 2 options here:\r\n- reopen app autmatically\r\n- apply new mode without relaunching app (preferable)\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/146227024-c72414c0-bfb3-4515-8373-397280d9b158.mp4\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n1) Open Status\r\n2) Change mode in device settings\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: 1.18 \r\n- Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Please, add logs/notes if necessary)\r\n\r\n",
